---
import Badge from "../components/Badge.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy policy"
  description="Privacy policy for PMD marketing and dashboard services."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-8 text-center shadow-card backdrop-blur">
      <Badge>Privacy</Badge>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate">
        This policy explains how PMD collects, uses, and protects information across the marketing site and the PMD dashboard.
      </p>
    </div>

    <Card class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Information we collect</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate">
        We collect the minimum data needed to operate PMD: account credentials, billing metadata, and usage data for analytics-only monitoring.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-slate">
        <li>Account data: email address, authentication tokens, and preferences.</li>
        <li>Billing data: subscription status and billing identifiers from our payment processor.</li>
        <li>Usage data: feature interactions, alert delivery metrics, and error logs.</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <Card class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">How we use data</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate">
        Data is used to deliver analytics-only alerts, secure the platform, and improve performance. We do not sell personal data.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-slate">
        <li>Operate and secure the PMD dashboard.</li>
        <li>Process subscriptions and account changes.</li>
        <li>Measure marketing and product performance.</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <Card class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Retention and security</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate">
        We retain data only as long as needed for operations and legal requirements. We use encryption and access controls to protect data.
      </p>
    </Card>

    <Card class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate">
        For privacy questions, contact support through your dashboard. PMD provides analytics only and does not offer financial advice.
      </p>
    </Card>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
